data.description: Discover your dream home in Sherman's prestigious Parkhaven Subdivision. This executive 3-bed, 3-bath gem on a third of an acre offers 2,614 sq ft of modern comfort and timeless elegance. Enjoy an extra large living room with a classic fireplace that beckons cozy evenings and warm conversations. The primary bedroom features a second fireplace, ensuite with skylights, and screened in porch access. An attached study provides the perfect space for focused work or leisurely reading. With a thoughtfully designed split bedroom arrangement, privacy is paramount for both residents and guests. The inclusion of two water heaters ensures a seamless flow of comfort, while an abundance of storage options in both the house and garage cater to all your organizational needs. This home includes a rain water harvesting system and A BRAND NEW ROOF was installed as of June 2023 and new flooring in the kitchen and breakfast area. Don't miss this opportunity for a fresh start!
